<%- include("./partials/header.ejs"); %>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="welcome-banner">
  <h2>Welcome to CoreCode;</h2>
  <div class="container">
    <div>
      <p>Welcome to CoreCode, where technology and fitness collide! This blog is your go-to destination for exploring the synergy between coding and workout strategies. Whether you're looking for tips to optimize your tech projects, innovative ways to enhance your fitness journey, or insights into how these two worlds intersect, CoreCode has you covered. Join me as I share coding tips, fitness hacks, and personal experiences that blend the best of both disciplines. Let’s push boundaries, break limits, and code a stronger future—together!</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <script src="https://unpkg.com/@dotlottie/player-component@2.7.12/dist/dotlottie-player.mjs" type="module"></script> 
      <dotlottie-player src="https://lottie.host/3a9fc389-d9d0-4d9a-9d15-599113330639/IPF95tXqkf.json" background="transparent" speed="1" style="width: 300px; height: 300px;" loop autoplay></dotlottie-player>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Recent Posts Section -->
<section class="recent-posts">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
    <div class="posts-grid">
      <% if (posts.length > 0) { %>
        <% posts.forEach(function(post) { %>
          <div class="post-card">
            <h3><a href="/post/<%= post.id %>"><%= post.title %></a></h3>
            <p><%= post.date %></p>
            <p><%= post.content %></p>
            <p>By: <%= post.author %></p>
            <a href="/post/<%= post.id %>" class="read-more">Read More</a>
          </div>
        <% }) %>
      <% } else { %>
        <p>No posts available. Be the first to create one!</p>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Explore CoreCode -->
<section class="explore-corecode">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Why Explore CoreCode?</h2>
    <div class="explore-card-container">
      <div class="explore-card">
        <h3>For Innovators</h3>
        <p>CoreCode isn’t just a blog—it’s a community for innovators who value both mental and physical strength. Here, you’ll discover practical coding tips to elevate your projects, fitness strategies to optimize your health, and unique insights that connect these two worlds. Whether you’re a tech enthusiast, a fitness lover, or both, CoreCode offers fresh perspectives and actionable advice to help you thrive. Dive in and find inspiration to push boundaries, unlock your potential, and create a balanced, high-performance lifestyle.</p>
        <a href="/blog" class="btn-explore">Explore Blog</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Call to Action -->
<section class="cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Want to Share Your Knowledge?</h2>
    <p>Feel inspired to write about fitness or tech? Create a post and share your insights with the CoreCode community!</p>
    <a href="/new-post">Create a New Post</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("./partials/footer.ejs"); %>
